V0140_01_00_00_0.text:
You're gonna defeat me?
Wanna put that theory to the test?

V0140_01_00_01_0.text: Don't you dare sell me short!

V0140_01_00_02_0.text: As my sweetie says, get your game on!

V0140_01_00_04_0.text: I can't believe I get to Duel my prince!

V0140_01_00_05_0.text: Alexis, I definitely don't want to lose against you!

V0140_01_00_07_0.text: Get your deck ready to see who's the best!

V0140_01_00_08_0.text: I'm ready to study super hard, Dr. Crowler!

V0140_01_00_09_0.text: I've come a long way to Duel you, Zane!

V0140_03_00_01_0.text: Maybe I'll end this Duel now!

V0140_05_00_00_0.text: When it comes to heart, I have more than anyone!

V0140_07_09_00_0.text: I flip over my Set card!

V0140_08_00_00_0.text: I activate the Equip Spell, Cupid's Kiss!

V0140_08_00_02_0.text: I activate the Equip Spell, Happy Marriage!

V0140_08_00_02_1.text: Watch what happens when my monsters say "I do!"

V0140_08_00_04_0.text: I activate the Spell Card, Monster Reincarnation!

V0140_08_00_05_0.text: I activate my Quick-Play Spell, Scapegoat!

V0140_08_00_06_0.text: I activate my Spell, Stray Lambs!

V0140_08_00_07_0.text: I activate my Spell Card, Where Arf Thou?!

V0140_08_00_08_0.text:
I activate my Equip Spell!
Trial of the Princesses!

V0140_08_00_09_0.text: By overcoming the trial, my monster becomes a princess!

V0140_08_00_10_1.text: I activate the Continuous Spell, Awakening of the Possessed!

V0140_08_00_11_0.text: Due to Awakening of the Possessed's effect, I draw one card!

V0140_08_00_12_0.text: I activate the Trap Card, Defense Maiden!

V0140_08_00_13_0.text:
Here's my Trap Card!
Beckoning Light!

V0140_08_00_14_0.text:
I activate my Trap Card!
Pikeru's Circle of Enchantment!

V0140_08_00_15_0.text:
You can't hide your secrets from me!
Pikeru's Second Sight!

V0140_08_00_16_0.text:
I activate my Trap Card!
A Rival Appears!!

V0140_08_00_18_0.text: Due to Unpossessed's effect, I Special Summon a monster!

V0140_08_00_19_0.text:
I activate my Trap Card!
Spiritual Earth Art - Kurogane!

V0140_08_00_20_0.text:
I activate my Trap Card!
Spiritual Water Art - Aoi!

V0140_08_00_21_0.text:
I activate my Trap Card!
Spiritual Fire Art - Kurenai!

V0140_08_00_22_0.text:
I activate my Trap Card!
Spiritual Wind Art - Miyabi!

V0140_08_00_23_0.text:
I activate my Trap Card!
Spiritual Light Art - Hijiri!

V0140_08_00_24_0.text:
I activate my Trap Card!
Dark Spirit Art - Greed!

V0140_09_00_00_1.text: I place a Maiden Counter on the monster that attacked her!

V0140_09_00_15_0.text: Aussa the Earth Charmer takes control of an EARTH monster!

V0140_09_00_16_0.text: Eria the Water Charmer takes control of a WATER monster!

V0140_09_00_17_0.text: Hiita the Fire Charmer takes control of a FIRE monster!

V0140_09_00_18_0.text: Wynn the Wind Charmer takes control of a WIND monster!

V0140_09_00_19_0.text: Dharc the Dark Charmer takes control of a DARK monster!

V0140_09_00_20_0.text: Lyna the Light Charmer takes control of a LIGHT monster!

V0140_11_01_00_0.text: I Summon a monster in Defense Position!

V0140_13_00_00_0.text: Get ready to fall head over heels!

V0140_13_00_01_0.text: Come on out, The Unhappy Girl!

V0140_13_00_14_0.text:
Ebon Magician Curran!
I'm counting on you!

V0140_13_00_33_0.text: I Special Summon a Sheep Token!

V0140_13_00_34_0.text: I Special Summon a Lamb Token!

V0140_16_00_01_0.text: There's nothing I won't do for love!

V0140_19_00_20_0.text: Wynn the Wind Charmer! Blow 'em away!

V0140_28_00_01_0.text: When my heart's in it, there's nothing I can't do!

V0140_28_00_02_0.text:
That was a great Duel!
Let's go at it again!

V0140_28_00_04_1.text: Thanks for getting your game on, sweetie!

V0140_28_00_05_1.text: That means Jaden's mine, not yours!

V0140_29_00_00_0.text: Just because I lost doesn't mean I didn't have fun!

V0140_29_00_01_0.text:
Noooo!
All my monsters are gone!

V0140_29_00_02_1.text: Not as amazing as my Jaden, but still amazing!

V0140_29_00_03_0.text: Why do I always end up behind?

V0140_29_00_04_0.text:
This Duel was great!
That's why you're my Jaden!

V0140_29_00_05_0.text: Seems you're my rival both on and off the field.

V0140_29_00_05_1.text: And I won't let you get rid of me that easily!

V0140_29_00_06_0.text:
I let this guy defeat me?
Sigh... I'm the worst.

V0140_29_00_07_1.text:
Just kidding!
You're still no Jaden!

V0140_29_00_08_0.text: I like your new look, Zane.

V0140_29_00_08_1.text: But Jaden is still the one for me!

V0140_33_00_00_0.text: I'm tough as I am cute!

V0140_33_00_02_0.text: You haven't seen the best of me yet!

V0140_30_00_00_0.text: What's the deal with you and Jaden?

V0140_30_00_01_0.text: Are you trying to woo him too?

V0140_30_00_02_0.text: Won't you let me into your heart?

V0140_34_00_00_0.text: No... I won't survive this attack!

V0140_34_00_05_0.text: This is a really fun Duel!

V0140_36_00_01_0.text: You're up! I know you got this!

V0140_36_00_02_0.text: Sorry for wasting our Life Points...

V0140_36_00_03_0.text: Win this for us, my prince!

V0140_36_00_06_0.text: The rest is up to you!
